panels.description: Shows rps for all requests that have been grouped in code via the k6 group("authn")  function

targets.query:
from(bucket: "k6")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "http_reqs")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "value")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["group"] == "::authn")
  |> drop(columns: ["_field", "scenario"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 1s, fn: count)
  |> sort(columns: ["status", "error_code"])
